  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E, F, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You carve glowing runes into your skin, creating a dormant seal that can be activated as an instant action. When activated, you gain a +2 competence bonus to a single Fortitude save, improved to +4 against a poison or disease effect, or DR 3/Chakra against a single physi- cal attack. The seal can be activated only if its bonus would be used immediately, and disappears afterwards.<br><br>You take 2 damage every time you attempt to perform this technique. Your body cannot carry more than one Fortitude seal.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend double the Chakra and double the damage dealt to you to double the bonuses granted. Doing so makes you unable to use this technique or Ketsuyoujutsu: Eibin for 24 hours.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
